Protection Layers:

| Layer                  | Mechanism                           | Response      |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------------- | ------------- |
| **Debugger Detection** | Timing analysis, console proxy      | Degrade       |
| **Code Integrity**     | Hash verification, signature checks | Shutdown      |
| **API Protection**     | Proxy wrapper on chrome.\* APIs     | Alert         |
| **Mutation Detection** | MutationObserver on DOM             | Alert         |
| **Timing Analysis**    | Interval consistency checks         | Degrade       |
| **Memory Protection**  | Object.freeze/seal                  | Self-destruct |


Integration Points:
Reads from checksums.json for verification
Reports to background script via SECURITY_EVENT messages
Degrades/disables on detection
Self-destruct for critical compromise